ained\npolicies transfer well to a real environment and can generalize to novel\nobjects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Apr 2022 17:55:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2022 07:36:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-01"}
