ed scheme's training overhead and computational cost do not grow with\nthe number of antennas, unlike previous work on enormous multiple-input\nmultiple-output (MIMO). The channel estimate scheme based on the physical\nproperties of the Large intelligent surface-based transceiver (LISBT)-assisted\nwireless communication systems is the subject of our future study.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Apr 2022 20:28:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 May 2022 09:15:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 10 May 2022 09:47:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-14"}
