iring kernel. Additionally, we compute the spin susceptibility in\nrelevant superconducting candidate phases and compare to recent neutron\nscattering and NMR Knight shift measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Apr 2022 14:49:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-07"}
